{"tid":1518132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[暗黑兵法］深紅計劃","createTime":"2019-08-30T06:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T11:19:00.000Z","uid":262084,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5d31b936d8d31590d8921935419c1cd81dca79c8","tid":1518132,"uid":262084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:56:59.000Z","msg":"今次政府高調捉黃之峰，周庭，陳浩天等，內地官媒快速高調報導，積極營造背後有外國勢力，金錢等援助，有預謀把示威活動抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n既然國家要我們愛國，再加上國慶來臨，我們便打算棄黑投紅，我地打算組成一隊100-200人既愛國團隊，團隊識別 - 紅衫，口罩，去警戒香港市民必需愛國，反對任何外國勢力在香港橫行。<br />\n<br />\n我地既目的係要喚起香港市民愛國情懷，尤其係對大躍進，文化大革命時對黨的「敬仰」，要廣大市民知道，沒有黨，你連屎都不是。我們更會配合政府大灣區宣傳，邀請一眾中老階層人士回大灣區養老退休，如有不從，被視爲不愛國者論，應當被教訓，改造。<br />\n<br />\n為免發生衝突，請黑衣人遠離我們，我們不喜歡你們，我們只會跟聲稱「愛國愛港」之人交流。我們亦會隨身自備鐵製指揮棒方便指揮，如有疑似黑幫想攻擊我等愛國者，我等必然會還擊之。我等愛國者將會揮舞著國旗，嚴肅核查所謂的「藍衣」愛國愛港者，到底是愛港多一點，還是愛國多一點。所謂物極必反，我相信大家都懂的。<br />\n<br />\n如大家有意加入愛國者計劃可在這裡留言。我們會看大家反應而決定是否實行計畫，TG group會稍後公怖。"},{"pid":"48141fa7bf562466e48aa984b1ff8be8e48a89bb","tid":1518132,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=d7e5da0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=bee58fa2\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=49e56267\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d7d3890dea072e18fa13db955de57cac3cafc59d","tid":1518132,"uid":226671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYsucAA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYsucAA.png&h=57b4b9dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1380ace1e04111690cf6b68af52a78be65a17647","tid":1518132,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"支持人大831決定<br />\n全面落實香港普選"},{"pid":"3cc3010fe981bf5375ae2f488e39c0463868587a","tid":1518132,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"文革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31da7fc6d8e6e05644209f07410dabeb4295b5e","tid":1518132,"uid":258159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"阻你一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AB7RqWd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAB7RqWd.jpg&h=4fa35189&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6Qzmyd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6Qzmyd.png&h=1355b1c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yHp8qZW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyHp8qZW.png&h=9c634639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=d7e5da